quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,96,"Walaw anna ahla alqura amanoowattaqaw lafatahna AAalayhim barakatinmina assama-i wal-ardi walakinkaththaboo faakhathnahum bima kanooyaksiboon"
  7,97,"Afaamina ahlu alqura an ya/tiyahumba/suna bayatan wahum na-imoon"
  7,98,"Awa amina ahlu alqura an ya/tiyahumba/suna duhan wahum yalAAaboon"
  7,99,"Afaaminoo makra Allahi falaya/manu makra Allahi illa alqawmu alkhasiroon"
  7,100,"Awa lam yahdi lillatheena yarithoonaal-arda min baAAdi ahliha an law nashao asabnahumbithunoobihim wanatbaAAu AAala quloobihimfahum la yasmaAAoon"
  7,101,"Tilka alqura naqussu AAalaykamin anba-iha walaqad jaat-hum rusuluhum bilbayyinatifama kanoo liyu/minoo bima kaththaboomin qablu kathalika yatbaAAu Allahu AAalaquloobi alkafireen"
  7,102,"Wama wajadna li-aktharihimmin AAahdin wa-in wajadna aktharahum lafasiqeen"
  7,103,"Thumma baAAathna min baAAdihim moosabi-ayatina ila firAAawna wamala-ihifathalamoo biha fanuthurkayfa kana AAaqibatu almufsideen"
  7,104,"Waqala moosa yafirAAawnu innee rasoolun min rabbi alAAalameen"
